name: Postcard from a Ghost
description: A piece based on handwritten graffiti tags and machinelearning: This image was generated by training a StyleGAN 1 model on <1000 images from a video sequence that shows my own handstyle written on paper with a blue sharpie. This image only shows one of the final letters. The ML model added shapes that were not in the original images and distorted many of the input shapes. 1024x1024px, PNG / Created by Alsino Skowronnek / 2019 / Instagram: @alsinoskowronnek
